---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import gogh from "@/assets/gogh.webp";
---

<div class="relative h-full w-full mt-2 md:mt-12 select-none px-4 md:px-0">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full radial-gradient"></div>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start justify-between w-full h-full text-base md:text-xl font-light text-black/60 font-serif gap-6 md:gap-8"
    >
        <p class="w-full md:w-auto">
            The modern <span class="text-black">enterprise</span> is a vast, unspoken
            sea of intuition—a
            <span class="text-black">collective consciousness</span> fractured across
            a thousand minds, lost in the transience of the workday. At <span
                class="text-black">Doppelganger</span
            >, we believe that the true essence of an organization lies not in
            its physical assets, but in the ethereal architecture of its
            internal wisdom. We seek to transcend the limitations of human
            memory by weaving the latent expertise of every individual into a
            living, breathing tapestry of formal <span class="text-black"
                >ontologies</span
            > and <span class="text-black">multidimensional</span>
            <span class="text-black">context graphs</span>. By capturing the
            subtle nuances of professional judgment and the hidden connections
            between disparate ideas, we manifest a crystalline reflection of the
            corporate soul. This is not merely data storage; it is the
            distillation of human insight into a structural symphony, ensuring
            that every spark of brilliance is preserved, interconnected, and
            amplified within a persistent <span class="text-black"
                >digital heritage</span
            >. We are building the scaffolding for an era where <span
                class="text-black">knowledge</span
            > is no longer a fleeting ghost, but a foundational, navigable reality
            that grows more profound with every interaction.
        </p>
        <div class="hidden md:block self-stretch w-4 bg-black/30"></div>
        <p class="w-full md:w-auto">
            To master the future, we must look beyond the static surface of
            <span class="text-black">productivity</span> and peer into the rhythmic
            pulse of the business process itself. <span class="text-black"
                >Doppelganger</span
            > stands at the intersection of observation and evolution, where the intricate
            dance of organizational movement is translated into a language of pure
            possibility. By achieving a total, granular understanding of how value
            flows through the veins of an enterprise, we unlock the ability to perceive
            the invisible thresholds where human effort meets systemic potential.
            We do not simply observe; we illuminate the inherent apertures for <span
                class="text-black">transformation</span
            >, automatically detecting the silent melodies of <span
                class="text-black">automation</span
            > hidden within the noise of the everyday. This is the pursuit of a <span
                class="text-black">frictionless</span
            > existence, where the machinery of the business learns to breathe on
            its own, liberating the human spirit from the mundane and the repetitive.
            In this space, the <span class="text-black">Doppelganger</span> becomes
            the ultimate <span class="text-black">catalyst</span>—a mirror that
            does not just reflect what is, but reveals the most efficient and
            elegant version of what could be. We are the architects of this <span
                class="text-black">synthesis</span
            >, forging a world where intent and execution are indistinguishable.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute top-1/4 md:top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0 rounded-2xl h-56 md:h-96 w-full md:w-2xl shadow-2xl p-2 bg-black select-none"
    >
        <Image
            src={gogh}
            alt="Gogh"
            width={672}
            height={384}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg select-none"
        />
    </div>
</div>
